## LocationQueryRaw type

Loose [LocationQuery](./reactivuety.locationquery.md) object that can be passed to functions like [Router.push](./reactivuety.router.push.md) and [Router.replace](./reactivuety.router.replace.md) or anywhere when creating a [RouteLocationRaw](./reactivuety.routelocationraw.md)
